gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਗੳੁਨੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਭੳੁਨੇ ॥
transliteration: Namo Sarab Gaddde|| Namo Sarab Bhaoune||
translation: Salutation to Thee O All-Pervasive Lord! Salutation of Thee O All-Permeator Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਰੰਗੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਭੰਗੇ ॥੨੨॥
transliteration: Namo Sarab Rane|| Namo Sarab Bhane||22||
translation: Salutation to Thee O All-loving Lord ! Salutation to Thee O All-destroying Lord!22.
Salutation to Thee O Death-destroyer Lord! Salutation to Thee O Beneficent Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Colourless Lord! Salutation to Thee O Deathless Lord! 23.
Salutation to Thee O Omnipotent Lord! Salutation to Thee O Doer Lord.
Salutation to Thee O Involved Lord! Salutation to Thee O Detached Lord!24.
Salutation to Thee O Kindredless Lord! Salutation to Thee O Fearless Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Generous Lord! Salutation to Thee O Merciful Lord!25.
Salutation to Thee O Infinite Lord! Salutation to the Thee O Greatest Lord!
Salutation to Thee O Lover Lord! Salutation to Thee O Universal Master Lord!26.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਸੋਖੰ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਪੋਖੰ ॥
transliteration: Namo Sarab Sokhan|| Namo Sarab Pokhan||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Destroyer Lord! Salutation to Thee O Sustainer Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਕਰਤਾ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਹਰਤਾ ॥੨੭॥
transliteration: Namo Sarab Kartaa|| Namo Srab Bartaa||27||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Creator Lord ! Salutation to Thee O Great Indulger Lord! 27.

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਜੋਗ ਜੋਗੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਭੋਗ ਭੋਗੇ ॥
transliteration: Namo Jog Joge|| Namo Bhog Bhoge||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Greatest Yogi Lord ! Salutation to Thee Great Indulger Lord!

gurmukhi: ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਦÎਾਲੇ ॥ ਨਮੋ, ਸਰਬ ਪਾਲੇ ॥੨੮॥
transliteration: Namo Sarab Diaale|| Namo Sarab Paale||28||
translation: Salutation to Thee O Gracious Lord! Salutation to Thee O sustainer Lord! 28.
